T1  - The labor-supply elasticity and borrowing constraints: Why estimates are biased
AU  - Domeij, David
AU  - Flodén, Martin
JO  - Review of Economic Dynamics
VL  - 9
IS  - 2
SP  - 242
EP  - 262
